query:
SELECT c.id, c.name, fl.id as floorId, fl.levelName, fl.isHidden, 
CASE WHEN fl.mapImageUrl IS NULL THEN 'NULL' 
     WHEN fl.mapImageUrl = '' THEN 'EMPTY' 
     ELSE SUBSTRING(fl.mapImageUrl, 1, 50) 
END as mapUrl
FROM shopping_centres c 
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON fl.centreId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Highlands%';
